{"tid":901580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【日俄親善】安倍赴新加坡　與普京磋商締結和平條約問題","createTime":"2018-11-14T06:31:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T00:17:34.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b3c8ace6227a2afafb00393a69dff03c60123ff1","tid":901580,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T06:31:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1428245_1_L_20181114131352.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1428245_1_L_20181114131352.jpg&h=9fe72bbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本首相安倍晉三啟程前往新加坡，出席東盟相關首腦會議，期間將於俄羅斯總統普京會面，預計將磋商兩國締結和平條約以及北方四島共同經濟活動問題。<br />\n<br />\n普京在兩個月前表明，期望日俄兩國在不設前提下，締結和平條約。安倍則主張先解決有主權爭議的北方四島歸屬問題。<br />\n<br />\n安倍在出發前表示，兩國都有解決和平條約問題的強烈意願，將透過好好對話切實讓談判有所進展，並基於早前達成共識的時間表切實推進共同經濟活動。"},{"pid":"696898a56abcbf0efe503771e851e2696d98d21b","tid":901580,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T06:36:12.000Z","msg":"又去中國, 又去俄國, 安倍真係當美國透明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a1a185642bd2565b7a848620c872f98032dae9","tid":901580,"uid":50776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T08:48:04.000Z","msg":"拎番4島就乜都簽啦"},{"pid":"65759cf2139552761fd7c3069728ccbc23aa6acf","tid":901580,"uid":149496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"696898a56abcbf0efe503771e851e2696d98d21b","tid":901580,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T06:36:12.000Z","msg":"又去中國, 又去俄國, 安倍真係當美國透明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T08:55:03.000Z","msg":"trump太惡 依家連法國佬都想飛起美國"},{"pid":"aed1e7aadfd6bf1f7bad89699182b80caa34743d","tid":901580,"uid":34666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65759cf2139552761fd7c3069728ccbc23aa6acf","tid":901580,"uid":149496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"696898a56abcbf0efe503771e851e2696d98d21